  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 : \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf , 3 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0bca\u0b95\u0bb5\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Wasp stings people who went to collect firewood: 1 dead, 3 hospitalized - incident in Pokavantalawai",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four people who went to collect firewood in forest area No. 17 in Bogavantlawa sub-division garden area have been bitten by wasps and one died and three others are receiving treatment in the hospital, said Bogavantlawa police. This incident took place yesterday (01) evening.",
        "When they went to forest area number 17 to collect firewood, an eagle attacked a wasp nest in a tree and the wasps dispersed and stung them.",
        "A medical officer of the hospital said that while all the four victims of wasp stings were admitted to the hospital, one of them died after being admitted to the hospital due to a severe attack.",
        "It has been revealed from the preliminary investigation of the police that the 50-year-old father of three children, Chikan Padmanathan, who belongs to Pokavantlawa lower division estate, died in the incident.",
        "Police added that the body has been kept in the mortuary of Pokavantala Hospital and the other three people who were bitten by the wasp are still undergoing treatment."
      ],
